OL,3,CMurder-accused mother: 'I got
OL,4,Cfrustrated but I never took it out on
OL,5,Cmy daughter'
OL,7,FA mother accused with her boyfriend of
OL,8,Fmurdering her toddler has told a court
OL,9,Fshe "got frustrated being a parent at
OL,10,Ftimes" but insisted she "never took it
OL,11,Fout" on her daughter.
OL,13,FIsabelle Welsh was two years old when
OL,14,Fshe collapsed at her home in Thornaby
OL,15,Fafter suffering a "massive head
OL,16,Finjury" in September 2025.
OL,18,FProsecutors say she was physically and
OL,19,Fsexually abused, and was found to have
OL,20,Fsuffered 21 broken bones in the weeks
OL,21,Fbefore she died last September.
OL,26,@qD@EOUrD@FO]rD@YOUsD@DO]wD@SOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
