PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784130494
OL,3,CMurder-accused mother: 'I got
OL,4,Cfrustrated but I never took it out on
OL,5,Cmy daughter'
OL,7,FHer mother, Alexandra Walker, 26, and
OL,8,FHarrison Simpson, 22, deny murder,
OL,9,Fallowing the death of a child, sexual
OL,10,Fassault and child cruelty.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday (15 July), Walker started
OL,13,Fgiving evidence in her trial at
OL,14,FTeesside Crown Court, tearfully
OL,15,Fdenying she had ever shaken Isabelle,
OL,16,Fbanged her against a wall or fractured
OL,17,Fher arm, leg, spine or skull.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
