OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784130494
OL,3,CMurder-accused mother: 'I got
OL,4,Cfrustrated but I never took it out on
OL,5,Cmy daughter'
OL,7,FShe said if she had seen anyone being
OL,8,Fviolent towards Isabelle she would
OL,9,Fhave "kicked them out of my house and
OL,10,Fphoned the police".
OL,12,FWalker told jurors the suggestion that
OL,13,Fshe had sexually abused Isabelle, or
OL,14,Fencouraged anyone to abuse her, had
OL,15,F"absolutely destroyed" her, saying her
OL,16,Fdaughter was "the person who meant
OL,17,Fmost to me in the world".
OL,26,@qD@FOUrD@RO]wD@AOUwD@VO]xD@NOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
