OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784130494
OL,3,CMurder-accused mother: 'I got
OL,4,Cfrustrated but I never took it out on
OL,5,Cmy daughter'
OL,7,FShe said becoming a mother was "the
OL,8,Fhappiest day of my life" and she felt
OL,9,F"unconditional love" when Isabelle was
OL,10,Fborn.
OL,12,FAsked about a conversation with a
OL,13,Ffriend in which she was said to have
OL,14,Fsworn about her daughter, Walker said:
OL,15,F"I'm very ashamed of saying those
OL,16,Fthings, especially after what's
OL,17,Fhappened, it was supposed to be a
OL,18,Fprivate conversation with a friend. I
OL,19,Fdidn't mean anything malicious by it."
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@XO]qD@AOUqD@TO]wD@AOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
