PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784130494
OL,3,CMurder-accused mother: 'I got
OL,4,Cfrustrated but I never took it out on
OL,5,Cmy daughter'
OL,7,FShe said she had been trying to wean
OL,8,FIsabelle off her dummy at the time,
OL,9,Fand the girl had been "more whingy
OL,10,Fthan usual".
OL,12,FWalker said: "I admit I got frustrated
OL,13,Fbeing a parent at times but I never
OL,14,Ftook it out on my daughter."
OL,16,FShe told the court she had been in
OL,17,Fabusive relationships before,
OL,18,Fincluding one with Isabelle's father,
OL,19,Fand her confidence was "not good" when
OL,20,Fshe met Simpson.
OL,26,@qD@WOUrD@KO]tD@NOUvD@\O]{D@XOU{D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
