OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784130494
OL,3,CMurder-accused mother: 'I got
OL,4,Cfrustrated but I never took it out on
OL,5,Cmy daughter'
OL,7,FWalker said he knew from her dating
OL,8,Fprofile that she had a child, and
OL,9,Finitially treated her "nicely" and her
OL,10,Fdaughter "kindly".
OL,12,FShe told jurors Simpson had pressured
OL,13,Fher to sell cannabis, and at one point
OL,14,Fshe stabbed herself with a knife to
OL,15,F"get out of selling drugs".
OL,17,FWalker said Isabelle's health
OL,18,Fdeteriorated after she met Simpson,
OL,19,Fbut she did not think he would harm
OL,20,Fher when he was alone with her.
OL,26,@qD@WOUqD@^O]rD@JOUrD@QO]wD@AOUwD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
