FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784130494
OL,3,CMurder-accused mother: 'I got
OL,4,Cfrustrated but I never took it out on
OL,5,Cmy daughter'
OL,7,FAsked who was most important to her
OL,8,Fbetween her daughter and her
OL,9,Fboyfriend, she replied: "Isabelle."
OL,11,FNicholas Lumley KC, defending Simpson,
OL,12,Fearlier told the court his client
OL,13,Fwould not be giving evidence.
OL,15,FThe trial continues.
OL,26,@qD@YOUqD@cO]
